short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AWS Service Health Dashboard timezone convert local timezone.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension that displays by converting to the time of the timezone of the local machine running the browser the time(PST) that is displayed in the Service Health Dashboard for AWS.
